# Banco de Tempo

## Description

A mobile app for managing appointments and time exchanges between users. It supports user registration, login, viewing and creating appointments, profile editing with photo upload, calendar integration, and smooth navigation.

## Technologies

- React Native with Expo  
- Firebase Authentication, Firestore, and Storage  
- React Navigation (Bottom Tabs, Stack Navigator)  
- Expo Image Picker  
- react-native-calendars  

